{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}LoneWolf chapitre {{p}}{% endblock %}

{% block header %}
    {{ include('entete/_entetehero.html.twig') }}    
{% endblock %}

{% block body %}

{# places dans l'inventaire #}
    {% set handItemCount = 0 %}
    {% set bpItemsCount = 0 %}
    {% for item in items %}
        {% if item.place is same as ('hand') %}
                {% set handItemCount = handItemCount + 1 %}
        {% endif %}
        {% if item.place is same as ('backpack') %}
            {% set bpItemsCount = bpItemsCount + 1 %}
        {% endif %} 
    {% endfor %}

<div>
    <p>
        You descend a flight of stone stairs that lead to a large chamber. A macabre sight awaits you. Directly opposite, across the large stone room, is an ornate archway with a corridor leading into the darkness beyond. The strange green light radiates from two lines of skulls each resting on a stone plinth. They face each other to form an eerie walkway across the room.
    </p>
    </br>
    <p>If you wish to walk across the room to the archway. 
            <a class="col-12 mt-5" href="
            {{ path('page_169', {'heroId':heroId }) }}
            ">
                <img class="fleches" src="{{ asset ('assets/img/ArrowR.png') }}" />
            </a>
            {# turn to 169. #}
    </p>
    </br>
    <p>If you wish to attack the skulls. 
            <a class="col-12 mt-5" href="
            {{ path('page_107', {'heroId':heroId }) }} 
            ">
                <img class="fleches" src="{{ asset ('assets/img/ArrowR.png') }}" />
            </a>
        {# turn to 107. #}
    </p>
</br>
</div>

{% endblock %}